Interface Dialog

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Expirable
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Dialog
extends Expirable
    Representation of a dialog. A dialog is a window that can be created, recalled or dismissed and can expire, that is indicate that it wants to be discarded and disposed of.
